beer.beer_description: Mr Danky the Christmas Brew is an easy-drinking American Pale. We've used Columbus and Chinook hops for a fresh pale ale that pours clear with a punchy pine aroma. Light citrus and grapefruit notes balance a gentle bitterness and earthy undertones. Howdy Ho Ho Ho!

items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!
